originalText.text: I parked in this lot for 4 hours and was charged $54 plus $10 in tax. Friendly staff but expensive for the location. I will look for a cheaper lot the next time I'm in town. It's a shame because it's the cleanest lot located closest to BBQs on 23rd street.
